              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">Golden Grain added "Our Brewing Story" page (Mike's journey from tech to brewing, 4-barrel system, local NC grains, water chemistry). Repeat customers increased 53%. Story = craft = love brand = return. 59% of breweries don't tell their story. Beer-seekers want to know: How do you brew? What ingredients? What's your philosophy? Generic brewery = commodity pricing. Story = craft = premium pricing = loyalty.</p>
